  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/7cc909e7585ace479f3fe3db2f5f6628.poster.avif?t=1753389396\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/7cc909e7585ace479f3fe3db2f5f6628.webm?t=1753389396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/7cc909e7585ace479f3fe3db2f5f6628.mp4?t=1753389396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is not one of those games where jumpscare is the key. There involves quite some reading in this game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Obscured Stories</strong> is a series about people haunted by what they’ve lived through. Each game uncovers a different story, pieced together from broken interviews, unsettling video tapes, and strange recordings. The truth is never clear — and some things are better left forgotten.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Resentment</strong> is a psychological horror game that follows Lisa Parker through a traumatic event.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As she is questioned by local police authorities, you will relive the events of that fateful evening as Lisa explains what happened.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lisa Parker is an international student living in Japan during the early 2000s. Working a part-time job at the SpinFuel Gas Station, her daily routine revolves around the mundane tasks of scanning products, restocking shelves, and maintaining the store. However, her quiet life begins to unravel when she starts noticing a mysterious man who seems to be watching her and the store from afar—over and over again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story-Driven Gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Customer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five endings. <strong>Decisions matter, so choose wisely!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two Nights: The game takes place over two nights.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pssst...<strong>BLOOP!</strong> :)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime:</strong> 40 - 60 minutes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/8cea5e87e6958e55bb8ff5b380a718b3.poster.avif?t=1753389396\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/8cea5e87e6958e55bb8ff5b380a718b3.webm?t=1753389396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/8cea5e87e6958e55bb8ff5b380a718b3.mp4?t=1753389396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/7cc909e7585ace479f3fe3db2f5f6628.poster.avif?t=1753389396\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/7cc909e7585ace479f3fe3db2f5f6628.webm?t=1753389396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/7cc909e7585ace479f3fe3db2f5f6628.mp4?t=1753389396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is not one of those games where jumpscare is the key. There involves quite some reading in this game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Obscured Stories</strong> is a series about people haunted by what they’ve lived through. Each game uncovers a different story, pieced together from broken interviews, unsettling video tapes, and strange recordings. The truth is never clear — and some things are better left forgotten.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Resentment</strong> is a psychological horror game that follows Lisa Parker through a traumatic event.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As she is questioned by local police authorities, you will relive the events of that fateful evening as Lisa explains what happened.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lisa Parker is an international student living in Japan during the early 2000s. Working a part-time job at the SpinFuel Gas Station, her daily routine revolves around the mundane tasks of scanning products, restocking shelves, and maintaining the store. However, her quiet life begins to unravel when she starts noticing a mysterious man who seems to be watching her and the store from afar—over and over again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story-Driven Gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Customer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five endings. <strong>Decisions matter, so choose wisely!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two Nights: The game takes place over two nights.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pssst...<strong>BLOOP!</strong> :)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime:</strong> 40 - 60 minutes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/8cea5e87e6958e55bb8ff5b380a718b3.poster.avif?t=1753389396\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/8cea5e87e6958e55bb8ff5b380a718b3.webm?t=1753389396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3544970/extras/8cea5e87e6958e55bb8ff5b380a718b3.mp4?t=1753389396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
